Hunspell-is - The Icelandic spelling dictionary project


Introduction
------------
This project aims to provide and maintain an Icelandic Hunspell spelling
dictionary. It's based on two sources: Jörgen Pind's wordlist from here
http://elias.rhi.hi.is/pub/is/ordalisti and the Icelandic Wiktionary Project,
http://is.wiktionary.org. Hunspell-is provides scripts to merge the sources.
New words are added _only_ through Wiktionary. Hunspell-is maintains a list of
banned words from the base wordlist file for removal.

Other languages can be added, see the langs/ folder.


General dependencies
--------------------
bzip2				http://www.bzip.org/
GNU awk				http://www.gnu.org/software/gawk/
GNU Bash			http://www.gnu.org/software/bash/
GNU ed				http://www.gnu.org/software/ed/
GNU Core Utilities		http://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/
GNU Wget			http://www.gnu.org/software/wget/
Hunspell			http://hunspell.sf.net/
iconv

Usage Instructions
------------------
makedict.sh list		lists supported languages
makedict.sh LANGUAGE		generates a dictionary for LANGUAGE, e.g. is
makedict.sh check		checks for dependencies
makedict.sh cleantmp		remove temporary files
makedict.sh cleandicts		removes dictionaries previously generated


Download Packages
-----------------
This is a list of projects using hunspell-is

